"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"icontxt textLink etacLink\" href=\"#\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\">",
"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Statistical model predicting survival in Budd-Chiari syndrome",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 421px; height: 313px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Survival for class I (n = 55), class II (n = 95), and class III (n = 55), according to the prognostic classification Ptrend &lt;0.0001, Pclass I versus II = 0.013, Pclass II versus III = 0.0001.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     The following equation was used to cacluate a hazard score:",
"     <br>",
"      1.27 X encephalopathy + 1.04 X ascites + 0.72 X prothrombin time + 0.004 X bilirubin",
"      <br>",
